    (find PC in (\TEDIT.FIRSTPIECE TEXTOBJ) suchthat (EQ OBJECT.PTYPE (PTYPE PC])

(\TEDIT.NEXT.OBJPIECE
  [LAMBDA (TEXTOBJ PC)                                       (* ; "Edited 24-Jul-2024 08:47 by rmk")
    (find old PC inpieces (NEXTPIECE PC) suchthat (EQ OBJECT.PTYPE (PTYPE PC])
)

